flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Initialize<br/>Shared Store]
    B --> C[Get User Input]
    C --> D{Exit<br/>Signal?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Display Final<br/>Statistics]
    D -->|No| F[Count Words<br/>in Input]
    F --> G[Update Shared Store<br/>text count / word count]
    G --> H[Compute Average<br/>Words per Text]
    H --> I[Display Running<br/>Statistics]
    I --> C
    E --> J([End])